    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[0]'
      value: In the smoke-choked reaches of the Empire, a man of standing does not
        simply die.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[1]'
      value: "House Ashworth built its fortune on the Continuance Act \u2014 the
        right to return, once, through means the Church calls unholy and the Registry
        calls law."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[2]'
      value: Edmund Ashworth never asked for the policy his family bought in his
        name.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[3]'
      value: But when the eastern rail line failed him, the policy activated without
        his consent.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[4]'
      value: Now he wakes in a stranger's ward, and the doctors are asking questions
        no dying man should have to answer twice.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
